{% block content %}

  <article>

    <header class="post-header">
      <div class="post-header-inner">
        <a href="/" class="post-breadcrumb">&larr; Back to Home</a>
        <h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
        <div class="post-meta">
          <span><strong>Freeland Marketing &amp; Entertainment</strong></span>
          <span>Everything you need to know before working with us</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </header>

    <div class="post-body">

      <h2>General</h2>

      <details class="faq-item" open>
        <summary>What types of businesses do you work with?</summary>
        <p>We work with businesses of all sizes — local shops, restaurants, service providers, e-commerce brands, and entrepreneurs, as well as mid-size companies and corporations. We also provide <a href="/services/ai-consulting/">AI consulting</a> and custom <a href="/services/ai-workflow-design/">AI workflow design</a> for businesses at every stage. If you want to grow, automate, or scale — we can help.</p>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>How soon will I see results?</summary>
        <p>Many clients see results within the first 30 days. <a href="/services/google-ads-management/">Google Ads</a> and <a href="/services/meta-ads/">Meta Ads</a> can drive leads within days. <a href="/services/seo/">SEO</a> builds over 3-6 months but compounds over time. <a href="/services/ai-lead-capture/">AI lead capture</a> starts recovering missed leads within the first week. We focus on measurable ROI from day one.</p>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>Do you require long-term contracts?</summary>
        <p>No. We earn your business every month through results. You stay because it is working — not because you are locked in. We are confident enough in what we deliver that we do not need to trap you in a contract.</p>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>How much do your services cost?</summary>
        <p>Pricing depends on your goals and the services you need. Our <a href="/services/ai-lead-capture/">AI lead capture</a> starts at $199/month. Marketing services are tailored to your budget — we have worked with everything from garage startups to established brands. The best way to get accurate pricing is to <a href="/#contact">book a free consultation</a>.</p>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>What makes Freeland Marketing different from other agencies?</summary>
        <p>Most agencies put you in a queue and send automated reports. We show up. Kevin personally works with every client, stays hands-on throughout the partnership, and combines marketing with AI automation — meaning we do not just drive traffic, we help convert and retain it too. Learn more on our <a href="/about/">About page</a>.</p>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>Do you work with businesses outside of Florida?</summary>
        <p>Yes. While we are headquartered in Palm Coast, FL, all of our digital marketing and automation services are delivered remotely to businesses anywhere in the United States. We serve clients across all 50 states.</p>
      </details>

      <h2>Marketing Services</h2>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>What marketing services do you offer?</summary>
        <p>We offer <a href="/services/social-media-management/">social media management</a>, <a href="/services/meta-ads/">Meta (Facebook/Instagram) Ads</a>, <a href="/services/google-ads-management/">Google Ads</a>, <a href="/services/seo/">SEO</a>, <a href="/services/website-design/">website design</a>, <a href="/services/creative-graphic-design/">graphic design</a>, <a href="/services/thumbnail-graphic-generation/">thumbnail and graphic generation</a>, <a href="/services/ecommerce-affiliate/">e-commerce and affiliate marketing</a>, and <a href="/services/influencer-affiliate/">influencer and affiliate program management</a>. We also build <a href="/services/affiliate-referral-automation/">automated referral programs</a>. See all services on our <a href="/services/">services page</a>.</p>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>Can you handle both my marketing AND automation?</summary>
        <p>Yes — that is our specialty. We offer full-service packages that combine <a href="/services/social-media-management/">social media management</a>, paid ads, <a href="/services/seo/">SEO</a>, and <a href="/services/ai-automation/">Freeland Automation</a> so everything works together as one unified growth engine. No juggling multiple vendors.</p>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>Do I need a website before starting marketing?</summary>
        <p>A website helps, but it is not required to get started. We can build you a <a href="/services/website-design/">fast, conversion-focused website</a> as part of your overall marketing package. Some services like social media management and paid ads can run without a website, though having one significantly improves conversion rates.</p>
      </details>

      <h2>AI Automation &amp; Lead Capture</h2>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>What is Freeland Automation?</summary>
        <p><a href="/services/ai-automation/">Freeland Automation</a> is our AI-powered service suite that automates your business operations — <a href="/services/crm-automation/">CRM follow-ups</a>, <a href="/services/email-marketing-automation/">email sequences</a>, <a href="/services/social-media-scheduling/">social scheduling</a>, <a href="/services/call-center-booking-automation/">call-center booking</a>, <a href="/services/lead-nurturing/">lead nurturing</a>, and more. If you are manually following up with leads, answering the same questions repeatedly, or losing customers because you are too busy to respond — you need it.</p>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>What is AI lead capture and how does it work?</summary>
        <p>Our <a href="/services/ai-lead-capture/">24/7 AI lead capture</a> system puts an AI assistant on your website and phone line that responds to every inquiry instantly — day or night. It answers questions about your business, qualifies leads, books appointments directly into your calendar, and follows up via SMS. Businesses see 20-40% more leads captured in the first month, mostly from after-hours traffic they were previously losing.</p>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>Will customers know they are talking to AI?</summary>
        <p>The AI is trained specifically on your business — your services, pricing, hours, and FAQs. It responds naturally and helpfully. Most customers prefer getting an instant, accurate response over leaving a voicemail and waiting. The system can hand off to a human team member at any time during business hours.</p>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>How many leads is my business losing after hours?</summary>
        <p>Studies show that businesses miss 20-40% of potential leads from after-hours inquiries, slow response times, and missed calls during busy periods. For a business generating $50,000 per month, that can translate to $10,000-$20,000 in lost monthly revenue. We can analyze your specific situation during a <a href="/#contact">free consultation</a>.</p>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>How fast is the setup for AI lead capture?</summary>
        <p>Most businesses are fully live within 5-7 business days. We handle all configuration, AI training, testing, and deployment. Many clients start capturing recovered leads within the first week.</p>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>Do I need to be technical to use your automation services?</summary>
        <p>Not at all. We handle all the technical setup, integration, and management. You tell us about your business and goals, and we build, configure, and maintain everything. We also provide training so your team knows how to use the systems we build.</p>
      </details>

      <h2>Working Together</h2>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>What does the onboarding process look like?</summary>
        <p>After your free strategy call, we map out a plan tailored to your business. Onboarding typically includes: a discovery session to understand your business, access setup for relevant platforms, strategy and system design, build and testing, and launch. Most clients are fully up and running within 1-3 weeks depending on the services.</p>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>How do I communicate with your team?</summary>
        <p>You work directly with Kevin and the team — no junior account managers, no ticket queues. We communicate via email, phone, and video calls. Most clients get same-day responses and we typically reply within 2 business hours.</p>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>What if I am not happy with the results?</summary>
        <p>We do not require contracts, so you can cancel at any time. That said, we work hard to deliver measurable results and maintain open communication throughout. If something is not working, we adjust the strategy — not wait for you to complain. Our goal is to make leaving the last thing you would ever consider.</p>
      </details>

      <div class="post-cta-box" style="margin-top:3rem;">
        <h3>Still Have Questions?</h3>
        <p>Book a free strategy call and we will answer every question you have about your business, our services, and what results you can expect.</p>
        <a href="/#contact" class="btn-primary btn-large">Book My Free Call &rarr;</a>
      </div>

      <p style="margin-top:1.5rem;text-align:center;">Or email us directly: <a href="mailto:kevin@freelandme.com">kevin@freelandme.com</a></p>

    </div>

  </article>

{% endblock %}
